description:
Danny welcomes Entertainment Tonight host/producer and Housewives expert Lauren Zima to Everything Iconic for a scene-by-scene breakdown the #RHONY boat ride from hell. They also touch on this week's #RHOC, Bachelor Nation, and lots more.
